WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.493
Introducing LangChain: The agent engineering platform for building AI-powered applications.

2
00:00:05.493 --> 00:00:15.295
LangChain simplifies the development of AI applications by providing tools and abstractions for chaining together interoperable components and third-party integrations.

3
00:00:15.295 --> 00:00:24.969
LangChain supports real-time data augmentation, model interoperability, rapid prototyping, and production-ready features like monitoring and debugging.

4
00:00:24.969 --> 00:00:30.139
To get started, simply install LangChain using pip or uv add. It’s that easy.

5
00:00:30.139 --> 00:00:38.937
Here’s a code snippet from `chat_models.py` showing how to initialize and interact with chat models, ensuring model interoperability.

6
00:00:38.937 --> 00:00:47.056
LangChain also includes a `.devcontainer` configuration for consistent development environments, making it easier for new contributors to get started.

7
00:00:47.056 --> 00:00:54.488
LangChain is built with Python and leverages popular frameworks and tools to provide a robust and flexible development experience.

8
00:00:54.488 --> 00:01:04.690
With 134,077 stars and 22,156 forks, LangChain is a widely adopted and trusted platform for building AI applications.

9
00:01:04.690 --> 00:01:16.835
Visit github.com/langchain-ai/langchain to start building your next AI application today. With LangChain, you’re just one pip install away from creating powerful AI agents.
